description:
Keydrop simulator is a recreation of a popular gambling website which is based around csgo skins.
My recreation contains all the main feautres of the original website such as: skin upgrader, case opening, selling skins, account profile and multiplayer case battles. It has operated for nearly half a year before being shut down amassing over that time 60 thousands registered accounts and 75 thousands page views in it's most popular day.

